# Flink Joiner POC


0. Install flink
   ```bash
    cd
    mkdir flinkPOC
    cd flinkPOC/
    wget http://apache.mirrors.ionfish.org/flink/flink-1.8.0/flink-1.8.0-bin-scala_2.11.tgz
    tar xzf flink-*.tgz
    cd flink-1.8.0
   ```

0. Start Flink (locally)

   ```bash
   ~/flinkPOC/flink-1.8.0/bin/start-cluster.sh
   ```
0. Stop Flink

   ```bash
   ~/flinkPOC/flink-1.8.0/bin/stop-cluster.sh
   ```

0. Build code

   sbt to compile code. Run this in IntelliJ Terminal: `sbt ~assembly`

   This will continually build

0. Run code

   execute `run_code.sh`

   Stop it by running `stop_code.sh`


# Resources

